{
  "texts": [
    "Despite this difference in experience, both evaluators have the same educational background (MD in community medicine).",
    "Adhering to the double-evaluation guidelines of the university to which the institute is affiliated, if there was a difference in marks of more than 33% awarded to a question by the two evaluators, a third evaluator (APG; assistant professor, MD in community medicine) was called in and their evaluation mark was considered to be the final score for that question.",
    "Qualitative Evaluation of ChatGPT ResponsesApart from scoring for the content, the evaluators assessed the responses to each question under three subdomains to further analyze the quality of ChatGPT responses: relevancy (\"Is the answer relevant to the prompt?",
    "\"), coherence (\"Is the description in the answer internally coherent?",
    "\"), and completeness (\"Does the answer sufficiently address all parts of the prompt?\")."
  ]
}